  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nJavaScript heap out of memory when upgrading truffle\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n```\r\nnpm uninstall -g truffle\r\nnpm install -g truffle\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nShould install newest truffle\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n```\r\n⸨#########⠂⠂⠂⠂⠂⠂⠂⠂⠂⸩ ⠹ idealTree: timing idealTree Completed in 168944ms\r\n<--- Last few GCs --->\r\n\r\n[9115:0x479d9a0]   520546 ms: Mark-sweep 2014.4 (2075.7) -> 2000.3 (2077.4) MB, 6365.1 / 43.8 ms  (average mu = 0.141, current mu = 0.098) allocation failure scavenge might not succeed\r\n[9115:0x479d9a0]   526912 ms: Mark-sweep 2016.5 (2077.4) -> 2004.1 (2081.2) MB, 5593.6 / 13.0 ms  (average mu = 0.131, current mu = 0.121) allocation failure scavenge might not succeed\r\n\r\n\r\n<--- JS stacktrace --->\r\n\r\nFATAL ERROR: Ineffective mark-compacts near heap limit Allocation failed - JavaScript heap out of memory\r\n 1: 0xa03520 node::Abort() [npm install truffle]\r\n 2: 0x94e471 node::FatalError(char const*, char const*) [npm install truffle]\r\n 3: 0xb7763e v8::Utils::ReportOOMFailure(v8::internal::Isolate*, char const*, bool) [npm install truffle]\r\n 4: 0xb779b7 v8::internal::V8::FatalProcessOutOfMemory(v8::internal::Isolate*, char const*, bool) [npm install truffle]\r\n 5: 0xd32245  [npm install truffle]\r\n 6: 0xd32dcf  [npm install truffle]\r\n 7: 0xd40e5b v8::internal::Heap::CollectGarbage(v8::internal::AllocationSpace, v8::internal::GarbageCollectionReason, v8::GCCallbackFlags) [npm install truffle]\r\n 8: 0xd44a1c v8::internal::Heap::AllocateRawWithRetryOrFailSlowPath(int, v8::internal::AllocationType, v8::internal::AllocationOrigin, v8::internal::AllocationAlignment) [npm install truffle]\r\n 9: 0xd130fb v8::internal::Factory::NewFillerObject(int, bool, v8::internal::AllocationType, v8::internal::AllocationOrigin) [npm install truffle]\r\n10: 0x105909f v8::internal::Runtime_AllocateInYoungGeneration(int, unsigned long*, v8::internal::Isolate*) [npm install truffle]\r\n11: 0x13ff079  [npm install truffle]\r\nAborted\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Ubuntu 20.04\r\n* Ethereum client:\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.4.8\r\n* node version (`node --version`): v14.14.0\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 7.20.6\r\n\r\nI tired to extend memory to 8gb via https://stackoverflow.com/questions/53230823/fatal-error-ineffective-mark-compacts-near-heap-limit-allocation-failed-javas  but didn't resolve my problem.",
